  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MkvAuthenticationProcessLogoutResult
    This enumeration is used for representing outcomes actions of a process logout request (for SAML / OpenID) Invoke MkvPlatform.createAuthenticationProcessLogoutRequest(com.iontrading.mkv.onbehalfof.api.MkvOnBehalfOfAuthenticationProcessLogoutRequest, com.iontrading.mkv.MkvAuthenticationProcessLogoutResponseListener) to validate the logout request and retrieve the external session reference and/or external user id of the session to unregister.
    MkvAuthenticationRequestCreationResult
    This enumeration is used for representing outcomes actions of an authentication request creation (for SAML / OpenID) Invoke MkvPlatform.createAuthenticationRequest(String, String, String, String, com.iontrading.mkv.MkvAuthenticationRequestCreationListener) to initiate the process and create an authentication request.
    MkvAuthenticationSingleLogoutRequestCreationResult
    This enumeration is used for representing outcomes actions of an authentication single logout request (for SAML / OpenID) Invoke MkvPlatform.createAuthenticationSingleLogoutRequest(String, String, String, String, String, String, String, String, MkvAuthenticationSingleLogoutRequestCreationListener) to initiate the process and create an authentication single logout request.
